{"TopicId":194031,"ForumId":38,"TopicTitle":"The Ten Commandments of Kerbal space program","CreatedByName":"Lewie","CreatedById":203745,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-05-21T01:41:22Z","PageNum":6,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Kerb24","CreatedById":214340,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-03T21:58:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThou shalt still try to continue the mission even if they are missing a component.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"StrandedonEarth","CreatedById":89439,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-04T02:39:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223834286\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022194031\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221596903880\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u00229\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Moach\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 8/8/2020 at 9:24 AM, Moach said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThou Shalt Useth MOAR BOOSTERS!!!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThou shalt also useth more struts!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n(not one mention of struts in this thread? tsk tsk....\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Admiral Fluffy","CreatedById":210816,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-04T02:48:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThou shalt not install launch escape systems, instead thou shalt only bail your Kerbals out with their parachutes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-04T05:48:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThou shalt keep playing 1.3.1 because your favourite mod stopped working in 1.7.3.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ColdJ","CreatedById":211123,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-04T06:19:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThou shalt get a purely solar power craft into orbit.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-04T06:29:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n... but your also can use wind generator in LEO.\u003Cbr\u003E\nThe wind speed is about 8 km/s there, it should work.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ColdJ","CreatedById":211123,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-04T06:37:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224051127\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022194031\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221636007380\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129408\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kerbiloid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 minutes ago, kerbiloid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n... but your also can use wind generator in LEO.\u003Cbr\u003E\nThe wind speed is about 8 km/s there, it should work.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI believe I have what is referred to as a Potato Computer, when it comes to these things, so unlikely currently to be playing with anything that simulates weather.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AtomicTech","CreatedById":210823,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-04T13:00:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThou shall install \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Engineer Redux (mod)\u0022\u003EKER\u003C/abbr\u003E as your first mod.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"adsii1970","CreatedById":89014,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-04T13:23:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224051109\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022194031\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221636004904\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129408\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kerbiloid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 hours ago, kerbiloid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThou shalt keep playing 1.3.1 because your favourite mod stopped working in 1.7.3.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUm, let me fix that...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThou shalt keep playing 1.3.0 because your favourite mod stopped working in \u003Cu\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E1.3.1.\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/u\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ColdJ","CreatedById":211123,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-04T14:04:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThou shalt only play 1.10.1 because I or one of the great modders can get most things working right in it, but everything after is a bit wonky.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerb24","CreatedById":214340,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-04T21:35:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThou shalt not try to figure out how to download mods and instead just play stock.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ColdJ","CreatedById":211123,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-05T06:03:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThou shalt build a pyramid out of Solid Rocket Boosters that throw your tiny 1 Kerbal capsule into a no return Kerbol orbit.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-05T07:10:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThou shalt let your Kerbals go.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ColdJ","CreatedById":211123,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-05T12:59:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThou shalt go back to a days old save if you lose one of them.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerb24","CreatedById":214340,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-05T19:49:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThou shalt turn on destroyable buildings.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jeb_Needs_A_Parachute","CreatedById":206461,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-06T03:38:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThough shalt make sure destroyable buildings is turned on, fail to destroy one, then realise you turned it off.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-06T05:18:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThou shalt plant flags and flag plants.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ColdJ","CreatedById":211123,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-06T08:24:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThou shalt memorise every witty loading saying.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-11-06T08:25:13Z\u0022 title=\u002211/06/2021 08:25  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003ENovember 6, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by ColdJ\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerb24","CreatedById":214340,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-06T13:08:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThou shalt do challenges.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ColdJ","CreatedById":211123,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-06T21:23:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThou shalt start a career game, then remember why you don\u0027t like playing career and go back to sandbox.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Admiral Fluffy","CreatedById":210816,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-06T23:55:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThou shalt try playing science mode, but with the tech tree completed.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-11-07T14:03:23Z\u0022 title=\u002211/07/2021 02:03  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003ENovember 7, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by Admiral Fluffy\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dr. Kerbal","CreatedById":207217,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-07T02:02:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThou shall strap more boosters if a rocket doesn\u0027t ascend.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"adsii1970","CreatedById":89014,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-07T02:04:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224052149\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022194031\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221636250573\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022207217\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Dr. Kerbal\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Dr. Kerbal said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThou shall strap more boosters if a rocket doesn\u0027t ascend.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd if that doesn\u0027t work, strap on moar boosters in asparagus fashion - and moar struts to hold \u0027em in place!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Admiral Fluffy","CreatedById":210816,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-07T02:44:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224052150\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022194031\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221636250654\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002289014\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022adsii1970\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n33 minutes ago, adsii1970 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd if that doesn\u0027t work, strap on moar boosters in asparagus fashion - and moar struts to hold \u0027em in place!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf even\u003Cem\u003E\u00A0that\u00A0\u003C/em\u003Edoesn\u0027t work, redesign the launch vehicle and try again.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRepeat until it works.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-07T04:24:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThou shalt use enough high launch clamps to be in space before launch.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}